Name: Super Goo Goo
About the game: Fling a ball of goo around a big open world and find stars. It's pretty simple. Let's have fun! FEATURES: Stuff it can stick to! Stuff it can bounce on! Fun gravity stuff! Open world! Secrets out the wazoo ;) Music & sound by Reckless All the sounds were made with his mouth (!!!)
